snippet.title: Rock Tour
snippet.description:
Get Rock Tour: http://www.bigfishgames.com/download-games/3520/rock-tour-game/index.html

Join Rock Tour and learn the cut-throat music business. A local band has what it takes to top the charts. Promote them and get them in the latest gear. Do you have what it takes to become a Rock Tour tycoon? Find out in this rockin' Time Management game.

  * Take charge of a local band
  * Outfit them in latest gear
  * Become a Rock Tour tycoon!

Play other great Tycoon Games at http://www.bigfishgames.com/download-games/genres/94/tycoon.html
